{"pageid":203691,"pagename":"The Forsaken Tower/Quick guide","title":"The Forsaken Tower/Quick guide","displaytitle":"The Forsaken Tower/Quick guide","revid":14248735,"properties":[{"name":"smw-semanticdata-status","value":""},{"name":"notoc","value":""},{"name":"description","value":"Congratulations, quest complete!"}],"content":"<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"messagebox\" style=\"\">\n<tbody><tr><td style=\"width: 50px;\"><div class=\"center\"><div class=\"floatnone\"><img alt=\"Instruction manual.png\" src=\"/images/Instruction_manual.png?13f14\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"28\" height=\"27\" data-file-width=\"28\" data-file-height=\"27\" /></div></div></td>\n<td><b>This quick guide has an <a href=\"/w/The_Forsaken_Tower\" title=\"The Forsaken Tower\">in-depth guide here</a>.</b><br style=\"clear: both;\" /><div style=\"font-size:0.85em; line-height:1.4em;\">It contains a more detailed description of dialogue, cutscenes, and storyline.\n</div></td>\n</tr></tbody></table>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Details\">Details</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/The_Forsaken_Tower/Quick_guide?section=1&amp;veaction=edit\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" title=\"Edit section: Details\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-divider\"> | </span><a href=\"/w/The_Forsaken_Tower/Quick_guide?action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Details\">edit source</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<table class=\"questdetails plainlinks\" cellspacing=\"3\"><tbody><tr><th class=\"questdetails-header\">Start point</th><td class=\"questdetails-info\"><img alt=\"Quest point icon.png\" src=\"/images/thumb/Quest_point_icon.png/17px-Quest_point_icon.png?dc356\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"17\" height=\"17\" srcset=\"/images/Quest_point_icon.png?dc356 1.5x\" data-file-width=\"21\" data-file-height=\"21\" /> Speak to <a href=\"/w/Lady_Vulcana_Lovakengj\" title=\"Lady Vulcana Lovakengj\">Lady Vulcana Lovakengj</a> in <a href=\"/w/Lovakengj\" title=\"Lovakengj\">Lovakengj</a>.</td></tr><tr><th class=\"questdetails-header\">Official difficulty</th><td class=\"questdetails-info\">Intermediate</td></tr><tr><th class=\"questdetails-header\">Description</th><td class=\"questdetails-info\">For thousands of years, the Wintertodt has remained safely sealed behind the great Doors of Dinh. Alas, despite the best attempts of the Lovakengj smiths and the Arceuus mages, the doors are failing. Only Dinh himself knew the secrets behind the creation of these doors. Without his knowledge, there may be nothing to stop the Wintertodt escaping and bringing ruin upon Kourend. It is up to you to recover this knowledge.</td></tr><tr><th class=\"questdetails-header\">Official length</th><td class=\"questdetails-info\">Short</td></tr><tr><th class=\"questdetails-header\">Requirements</th><td class=\"questdetails-info qc-input qc-active\">\n<ul><li>Completion of the following quests:\n<ul><li><a href=\"/w/Client_of_Kourend\" title=\"Client of Kourend\">Client of Kourend</a>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/w/X_Marks_the_Spot\" title=\"X Marks the Spot\">X Marks the Spot</a></li></ul></li></ul></li>\n<li>20% <a href=\"/w/Lovakengj_favour\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Lovakengj favour\">Lovakengj favour</a></li></ul></td></tr><tr><th class=\"questdetails-header\">Items required</th><td class=\"questdetails-info\">\n<div class=\"lighttable checklist no-toggle-parent\">\n<ul><li><a href=\"/w/Tinderbox\" title=\"Tinderbox\">Tinderbox</a> (obtainable during quest)</li></ul></div></td></tr><tr><th class=\"questdetails-header\">Recommended</th><td class=\"questdetails-info qc-active\">\n<div class=\"lighttable checklist no-toggle-parent\">\n<ul><li><a href=\"/w/Antipoison\" title=\"Antipoison\">Antipoison</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/w/Food\" title=\"Food\">Food</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/w/Games_necklace\" title=\"Games necklace\">Games necklace</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/w/Battlefront_teleport\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Battlefront teleport\">Battlefront teleport</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/w/Xeric%27s_talisman\" title=\"Xeric&#39;s talisman\">Xeric's talisman</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/w/Stamina_potion\" title=\"Stamina potion\">Stamina potion</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/w/Dramen_Staff\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Dramen Staff\">Dramen Staff</a> or <a href=\"/w/Lunar_Staff\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Lunar Staff\">Lunar Staff</a></li>\n<li>Bring 6 <a href=\"/w/Coal\" title=\"Coal\">Coal</a> and 1 <a href=\"/w/Adamantite_ore\" title=\"Adamantite ore\">Adamantite ore</a> to complete a <a href=\"/w/Hard_Kourend_%26_Kebos_Diary\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Hard Kourend &amp; Kebos Diary\">Hard Kourend &amp; Kebos Diary</a> task (requires <span class=\"scp\" data-skill=\"Smithing\" data-level=\"70\"><a href=\"/w/Smithing\" title=\"Smithing\"><img alt=\"Smithing\" src=\"/images/Smithing_icon.png?d26c5\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"21\" height=\"21\" data-file-width=\"19\" data-file-height=\"19\" /></a> 70 <a href=\"/w/Smithing\" title=\"Smithing\">Smithing</a></span> <sup>(<span title=\"This requirement is boostable\" style=\"cursor:help; text-decoration: underline dotted;\">boostable</span>)</sup>)</li></ul></div></td></tr><tr><th class=\"questdetails-header\">Enemies to defeat</th><td class=\"questdetails-info\">\nNone</td></tr></tbody></table><div class=\"hidden\" style=\"display:none\">&#123;&#34;requirements&#34;:&#34;*Completion of the following quests:\\n**&#91;&#91;Client of Kourend&#93;&#93;\\n***&#91;&#91;X Marks the Spot&#93;&#93;\\n*20% &#91;&#91;Lovakengj favour&#93;&#93;&#34;,&#34;desc&#34;:&#34;For thousands of years, the Wintertodt has remained safely sealed behind the great Doors of Dinh. Alas, despite the best attempts of the Lovakengj smiths and the Arceuus mages, the doors are failing. Only Dinh himself knew the secrets behind the creation of these doors. Without his knowledge, there may be nothing to stop the Wintertodt escaping and bringing ruin upon Kourend. It is up to you to recover this knowledge.&#34;,&#34;difficulty&#34;:&#34;Intermediate&#34;,&#34;kills&#34;:&#34;None&#34;,&#34;name&#34;:&#34;The Forsaken Tower/Quick guide&#34;,&#34;start&#34;:&#34;Speak to &#91;&#91;Lady Vulcana Lovakengj&#93;&#93; in &#91;&#91;Lovakengj&#93;&#93;.&#34;,&#34;length&#34;:&#34;Short&#34;,&#34;items&#34;:&#34;*&#91;&#91;Tinderbox&#93;&#93; (obtainable during quest)&#34;&#125;</div>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Walkthrough\">Walkthrough</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/The_Forsaken_Tower/Quick_guide?section=2&amp;veaction=edit\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" title=\"Edit section: Walkthrough\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-divider\"> | </span><a href=\"/w/The_Forsaken_Tower/Quick_guide?action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: Walkthrough\">edit source</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Start\">Start</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/The_Forsaken_Tower/Quick_guide?section=3&amp;veaction=edit\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" title=\"Edit section: Start\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-divider\"> | </span><a href=\"/w/The_Forsaken_Tower/Quick_guide?action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: Start\">edit source</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<div class=\"lighttable checklist\">\n<ul><li>Talk to <a href=\"/w/Lady_Vulcana_Lovakengj\" title=\"Lady Vulcana Lovakengj\">Lady Vulcana Lovakengj</a> in the <a href=\"/w/Lovakengj_Assembly\" title=\"Lovakengj Assembly\">Lovakengj Assembly</a> building to the west of the southern bank. <span class=\"chat-options\">(<i title=\"Chat options\"><img alt=\"Chat\" src=\"/images/Quick_chat_button.png?cf91b\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"13\" height=\"10\" data-file-width=\"13\" data-file-height=\"10\" /></i> <span class=\"chat-options-underline\" title=\"Yes.\">1</span>&#8226;<span class=\"chat-options-underline\" title=\"I&#39;ll get going.\">3</span>)</span><span class=\"hidden js-tooltip-click\" data-tooltip-name=\"c_option-32e4036f2a996f5a1110dd77dcbc2a2e\" style=\"display:none;color:grey;background:none;border:none\"><b>&#8230;</b></span><div class=\"hidden js-tooltip-wrapper\" data-tooltip-limit-width=\"yes\" data-tooltip-arrow-size=\"10\" data-tooltip-for=\"c_option-32e4036f2a996f5a1110dd77dcbc2a2e\" data-tooltip-arrow=\"yes\" style=\"display:none;padding:0\"><div class=\"js-tooltip-text\"><table><tbody><tr><td><b>1</b></td><td>Yes.</td></tr><tr><td><b>3</b></td><td>I'll get going.</td></tr></tbody></table></div></div></li>\n<li>Go to the <a href=\"/w/Wintertodt\" title=\"Wintertodt\">Wintertodt</a> camp (<a href=\"/w/Games_necklace\" title=\"Games necklace\">Games necklace</a> teleport).\n<ul><li>Talk to <a href=\"/w/Ignisia\" title=\"Ignisia\">Ignisia</a> in the north-east of the camp if you haven't previously done so.</li></ul></li>\n<li>Talk to the dwarf <a href=\"/w/Undor\" title=\"Undor\">Undor</a> inside the camp. <span class=\"chat-options\">(<i title=\"Chat options\"><img alt=\"Chat\" src=\"/images/Quick_chat_button.png?cf91b\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"13\" height=\"10\" data-file-width=\"13\" data-file-height=\"10\" /></i> <span class=\"chat-options-underline\" title=\"I&#39;ve been sent to help you.\">4</span>)</span><span class=\"hidden js-tooltip-click\" data-tooltip-name=\"c_option-428878c5300e9fcb39566f25a55b4118\" style=\"display:none;color:grey;background:none;border:none\"><b>&#8230;</b></span><div class=\"hidden js-tooltip-wrapper\" data-tooltip-limit-width=\"yes\" data-tooltip-arrow-size=\"10\" data-tooltip-for=\"c_option-428878c5300e9fcb39566f25a55b4118\" data-tooltip-arrow=\"yes\" style=\"display:none;padding:0\"><div class=\"js-tooltip-text\"><table><tbody><tr><td><b>4</b></td><td>I've been sent to help you.</td></tr></tbody></table></div></div>\n<ul><li>If he tells you to talk to the \"Fiery lass\" Talk to Ignisia just to the north east, before returning to him.</li></ul></li></ul>\n</div>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"The_Hammer\">The Hammer</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/The_Forsaken_Tower/Quick_guide?section=4&amp;veaction=edit\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" title=\"Edit section: The Hammer\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-divider\"> | </span><a href=\"/w/The_Forsaken_Tower/Quick_guide?action=edit&amp;section=4\" title=\"Edit section: The Hammer\">edit source</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<h4><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Powergrid\">Powergrid</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/The_Forsaken_Tower/Quick_guide?section=5&amp;veaction=edit\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" title=\"Edit section: Powergrid\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-divider\"> | </span><a href=\"/w/The_Forsaken_Tower/Quick_guide?action=edit&amp;section=5\" title=\"Edit section: Powergrid\">edit source</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h4>\n<div class=\"lighttable checklist\">\n<ul><li>Go to <a href=\"/w/The_Forsaken_Tower_(location)\" title=\"The Forsaken Tower (location)\">The Forsaken Tower</a> to the east of <a href=\"/w/Mount_Karuulm\" title=\"Mount Karuulm\">Mount Karuulm</a>, west of <a href=\"/w/Lovakengj\" title=\"Lovakengj\">Lovakengj</a> (north-east of fairy ring <span class=\"fairycode\"><b>c</b><b>i</b><b>r</b></span>, <a href=\"/w/Battlefront_Teleport\" title=\"Battlefront Teleport\">Battlefront Teleport</a> or <a href=\"/w/Skills_necklace\" title=\"Skills necklace\">Skills necklace</a> to Farming Guild).</li>\n<li>Inspect the Display Case.</li>\n<li>Go down the ladder behind the Display Case and open the north-eastern door. Search the north-north-east crate for a <a href=\"/w/Generator_crank\" title=\"Generator crank\">generator crank</a>.</li>\n<li>Inspect the steam generator in the south. <span class=\"chat-options\">(<i title=\"Chat options\"><img alt=\"Chat\" src=\"/images/Quick_chat_button.png?cf91b\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"13\" height=\"10\" data-file-width=\"13\" data-file-height=\"10\" /></i> <span class=\"chat-options-underline\" title=\"Start the generator.\">1</span>)</span><span class=\"hidden js-tooltip-click\" data-tooltip-name=\"c_option-26637732337128fdf4548782661f2e47\" style=\"display:none;color:grey;background:none;border:none\"><b>&#8230;</b></span><div class=\"hidden js-tooltip-wrapper\" data-tooltip-limit-width=\"yes\" data-tooltip-arrow-size=\"10\" data-tooltip-for=\"c_option-26637732337128fdf4548782661f2e47\" data-tooltip-arrow=\"yes\" style=\"display:none;padding:0\"><div class=\"js-tooltip-text\"><table><tbody><tr><td><b>1</b></td><td>Start the generator.</td></tr></tbody></table></div></div>\n<ul><li>Start the generator.</li></ul></li>\n<li>Inspect the Power Grid. <span class=\"chat-options\">(<i title=\"Chat options\"><img alt=\"Chat\" src=\"/images/Quick_chat_button.png?cf91b\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"13\" height=\"10\" data-file-width=\"13\" data-file-height=\"10\" /></i> <span class=\"chat-options-underline\" title=\"Yes.\">1</span>)</span><span class=\"hidden js-tooltip-click\" data-tooltip-name=\"c_option-97718ef27c50d6807e0348bd0128984b\" style=\"display:none;color:grey;background:none;border:none\"><b>&#8230;</b></span><div class=\"hidden js-tooltip-wrapper\" data-tooltip-limit-width=\"yes\" data-tooltip-arrow-size=\"10\" data-tooltip-for=\"c_option-97718ef27c50d6807e0348bd0128984b\" data-tooltip-arrow=\"yes\" style=\"display:none;padding:0\"><div class=\"js-tooltip-text\"><table><tbody><tr><td><b>1</b></td><td>Yes.</td></tr></tbody></table></div></div>\n<ul><li>Align the Power Grid as shown below.</li></ul></li></ul>\n</div>\n<div class=\"center\"><div class=\"floatnone\"><a href=\"/w/File:The_Forsaken_Tower_-_Powergrid_solution.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"The Forsaken Tower - Powergrid solution.png\" src=\"/images/The_Forsaken_Tower_-_Powergrid_solution.png?994f8\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"326\" height=\"324\" data-file-width=\"326\" data-file-height=\"324\" /></a></div></div>\n<h4><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Furnace\">Furnace</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/The_Forsaken_Tower/Quick_guide?section=6&amp;veaction=edit\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" title=\"Edit section: Furnace\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-divider\"> | </span><a href=\"/w/The_Forsaken_Tower/Quick_guide?action=edit&amp;section=6\" title=\"Edit section: Furnace\">edit source</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h4>\n<div class=\"lighttable checklist\">\n<ul><li>Go up the ladder and then into the northern room. Search the cupboards for a <a href=\"/w/Tinderbox\" title=\"Tinderbox\">tinderbox</a>, <a href=\"/w/5-gallon_jug\" title=\"5-gallon jug\">5-gallon jug</a>, and <a href=\"/w/8-gallon_jug\" title=\"8-gallon jug\">8-gallon jug</a>.\n<ul><li>Fill the 5-gallon jug with coolant through the coolant dispenser in the west.</li>\n<li>Use the 5-gallon jug on the empty 8 gallon jug.</li>\n<li>Fill the 5-gallon jug with coolant.</li>\n<li>Use the 5-gallon jug on the 8 gallon jug.</li>\n<li>Empty the 8 gallon jug (right-click check).</li>\n<li>Use the 5-gallon jug on the empty 8 gallon jug (there should be 2 gallons in the jug).</li>\n<li>Fill the 5-gallon jug with coolant.</li>\n<li>Use the 5-gallon jug on the 8 gallon jug.</li>\n<li>Fill the 5-gallon jug with coolant.</li>\n<li>Use the 5-gallon jug on the 8 gallon jug.</li>\n<li>You should now have 4 gallons of coolant in the 5-gallon jug. Use it on the furnace coolant west of the furnace, then light the furnace with the tinderbox.</li></ul></li>\n<li>If doing the diary task, smelt the <a href=\"/w/Adamantite_bar\" title=\"Adamantite bar\">adamantite bar</a> now.</li></ul>\n</div>\n<h4><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Potion\">Potion</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/The_Forsaken_Tower/Quick_guide?section=7&amp;veaction=edit\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" title=\"Edit section: Potion\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-divider\"> | </span><a href=\"/w/The_Forsaken_Tower/Quick_guide?action=edit&amp;section=7\" title=\"Edit section: Potion\">edit source</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h4>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:302px;\"><a href=\"/w/File:The_Forsaken_Tower_-_old_notes_explanation.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/thumb/The_Forsaken_Tower_-_old_notes_explanation.png/300px-The_Forsaken_Tower_-_old_notes_explanation.png?5b6ac\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"300\" height=\"266\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/The_Forsaken_Tower_-_old_notes_explanation.png/450px-The_Forsaken_Tower_-_old_notes_explanation.png?5b6ac 1.5x, /images/The_Forsaken_Tower_-_old_notes_explanation.png?5b6ac 2x\" data-file-width=\"490\" data-file-height=\"435\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/w/File:The_Forsaken_Tower_-_old_notes_explanation.png\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>A visual explanation of the solution.</div></div></div>\n<div class=\"lighttable checklist\">\n<ul><li>Go upstairs.</li>\n<li>Open the door, then take the notes from the eastern cupboard.</li>\n<li>Take the cleansing fluid from the northern table. <b>The position will be random for everyone.</b> Look at the notes to see the riddle: the fluids are listed in order of 1-2-3-4-5 (e.g. if cleansing fluid is the second potion mentioned in the fourth sentence, it is number 5).\n<ul><li><b>Warning</b>: If you choose the wrong potion, you will take high damage (25+) and become poisoned. This can be avoided by logging out before advancing the dialogue.</li></ul></li>\n<li>Use the cleansing fluid on the refinery to the south, then activate it <span class=\"chat-options\">(<i title=\"Chat options\"><img alt=\"Chat\" src=\"/images/Quick_chat_button.png?cf91b\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"13\" height=\"10\" data-file-width=\"13\" data-file-height=\"10\" /></i> <span class=\"chat-options-underline\" title=\"Yes.\">1</span>&#8226;<span class=\"chat-options-underline\" title=\"Yes.\">1</span>)</span><span class=\"hidden js-tooltip-click\" data-tooltip-name=\"c_option-44a6856aa740822f56279d9ff9562fc2\" style=\"display:none;color:grey;background:none;border:none\"><b>&#8230;</b></span><div class=\"hidden js-tooltip-wrapper\" data-tooltip-limit-width=\"yes\" data-tooltip-arrow-size=\"10\" data-tooltip-for=\"c_option-44a6856aa740822f56279d9ff9562fc2\" data-tooltip-arrow=\"yes\" style=\"display:none;padding:0\"><div class=\"js-tooltip-text\"><table><tbody><tr><td><b>1</b></td><td>Yes.</td></tr><tr><td><b>1</b></td><td>Yes.</td></tr></tbody></table></div></div></li></ul>\n</div>\n<h4><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Altar\">Altar</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/The_Forsaken_Tower/Quick_guide?section=8&amp;veaction=edit\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" title=\"Edit section: Altar\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-divider\"> | </span><a href=\"/w/The_Forsaken_Tower/Quick_guide?action=edit&amp;section=8\" title=\"Edit section: Altar\">edit source</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h4>\n<div class=\"lighttable checklist\">\n<ul><li>Go up the ladder.</li>\n<li>There are four discs. In the following order, remove a disc from a pylon and place it on another pylon:\n<ul><li>From West <b>(W)</b> to East <b>(E)</b></li>\n<li>From <b>W</b> to Centre <b>(C)</b></li>\n<li>From <b>E</b> to <b>C</b></li>\n<li>From <b>W</b> to <b>E</b></li>\n<li>From <b>C</b> to <b>W</b></li>\n<li>From <b>C</b> to <b>E</b></li>\n<li>From <b>W</b> to <b>E</b></li>\n<li>From <b>W</b> to <b>C</b></li>\n<li>From <b>E</b> to <b>C</b></li>\n<li>From <b>E</b> to <b>W</b></li>\n<li>From <b>C</b> to <b>W</b></li>\n<li>From <b>E</b> to <b>C</b></li>\n<li>From <b>W</b> to <b>E</b></li>\n<li>From <b>W</b> to <b>C</b></li>\n<li>From <b>E</b> to <b>C</b></li></ul></li>\n<li>Go downstairs and get Dinh's hammer from the display case.</li></ul>\n</div>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Finishing_up\">Finishing up</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/The_Forsaken_Tower/Quick_guide?section=9&amp;veaction=edit\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" title=\"Edit section: Finishing up\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-divider\"> | </span><a href=\"/w/The_Forsaken_Tower/Quick_guide?action=edit&amp;section=9\" title=\"Edit section: Finishing up\">edit source</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<div class=\"lighttable checklist\">\n<ul><li>Return to <a href=\"/w/Wintertodt_Camp\" title=\"Wintertodt Camp\">Wintertodt Camp</a>.</li>\n<li>Use the hammer on <a href=\"/w/Undor\" title=\"Undor\">Undor</a>.</li>\n<li>Return to <a href=\"/w/Lady_Vulcana_Lovakengj\" title=\"Lady Vulcana Lovakengj\">Lady Vulcana Lovakengj</a>.</li></ul>\n</div>\n<p><b>Congratulations, quest complete!</b>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Rewards\">Rewards</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/The_Forsaken_Tower/Quick_guide?section=10&amp;veaction=edit\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" title=\"Edit section: Rewards\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-divider\"> | </span><a href=\"/w/The_Forsaken_Tower/Quick_guide?action=edit&amp;section=10\" title=\"Edit section: Rewards\">edit source</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"center\"><div class=\"floatnone\"><a href=\"/w/File:The_Forsaken_Tower_reward_scroll.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"The Forsaken Tower reward scroll.png\" src=\"/images/The_Forsaken_Tower_reward_scroll.png?17680\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"488\" height=\"320\" data-file-width=\"488\" data-file-height=\"320\" /></a></div></div>\n<ul><li>1 <a href=\"/w/Quest_points\" title=\"Quest points\"><img alt=\"Quest points\" src=\"/images/Quest_point_icon.png?dc356\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"21\" height=\"21\" data-file-width=\"21\" data-file-height=\"21\" /></a>  <a href=\"/w/Quest_points\" title=\"Quest points\">Quest point</a></li>\n<li><span class=\"scp\" data-skill=\"Mining\" data-level=\"500\"><a href=\"/w/Mining\" title=\"Mining\"><img alt=\"Mining\" src=\"/images/thumb/Mining_icon.png/21px-Mining_icon.png?00870\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"21\" height=\"21\" srcset=\"/images/Mining_icon.png?00870 1.5x\" data-file-width=\"23\" data-file-height=\"23\" /></a> 500 </span> <a href=\"/w/Mining\" title=\"Mining\">Mining</a> experience</li>\n<li><span class=\"scp\" data-skill=\"Smithing\" data-level=\"500\"><a href=\"/w/Smithing\" title=\"Smithing\"><img alt=\"Smithing\" src=\"/images/Smithing_icon.png?d26c5\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"21\" height=\"21\" data-file-width=\"19\" data-file-height=\"19\" /></a> 500 </span> <a href=\"/w/Smithing\" title=\"Smithing\">Smithing</a> experience</li>\n<li>6,000 <a href=\"/w/Coins\" title=\"Coins\">coins</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/w/Lovakengj_favour_certificate\" title=\"Lovakengj favour certificate\">Lovakengj favour certificate</a>. Reading it grants 10% <a href=\"/w/Lovakengj_favour\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Lovakengj favour\">Lovakengj favour</a>.</li>\n<li>A page for <a href=\"/w/Kharedst%27s_memoirs\" title=\"Kharedst&#39;s memoirs\">Kharedst's memoirs</a>, '<a href=\"/w/Jewellery_of_jubilation\" title=\"Jewellery of jubilation\">Jewellery of jubilation</a>.' It teleports players north-east of the bank in Lovakengj.</li></ul>\n<table class=\"navbox nowraplinks mw-collapsible\" data-expandtext=\"show\" data-navbox-name=\"The Forsaken Tower\" data-collapsetext=\"hide\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" class=\"navbox-title\" id=\"navbox-title\"><div class=\"navbox-title-name-notplain\"><div class=\"navbar\" style=\"float:left;text-align:left;width:6em\"><div class=\"plainlinks noprint\" style=\"background-color:transparent;padding:0;font-weight:normal;font-size:xx-small;white-space:nowrap\"><a href=\"/w/Template:The_Forsaken_Tower\" title=\"Template:The Forsaken Tower\"><span title=\"View this template\">v</span></a>&#160;<span style=\"font-size:80%\">&#8226;</span>&#160;<a class=\"text\" href=\"https://oldschool.runescape.wiki/w/Template_talk:The_Forsaken_Tower\"><span title=\"Discussion about this template\">d</span></a>&#160;<span style=\"font-size:80%\">&#8226;</span>&#160;<a class=\"text\" href=\"https://oldschool.runescape.wiki/w/Template:The_Forsaken_Tower?action=edit\"><span title=\"Edit this template\">e</span></a></div></div><span><a href=\"/w/The_Forsaken_Tower\" title=\"The Forsaken Tower\">The Forsaken Tower</a></span></div></th></tr><tr class=\"navbox-group\"><td class=\"navbox-group-title\">NPCs</td><td class=\"navbox-list\">\n<ul><li><span class=\"plink-template\"><a href=\"/w/Lady_Vulcana_Lovakengj\" title=\"Lady Vulcana Lovakengj\"><img alt=\"Lady Vulcana Lovakengj chathead.png: Chat head image of Lady Vulcana Lovakengj\" src=\"/images/thumb/Lady_Vulcana_Lovakengj_chathead.png/24px-Lady_Vulcana_Lovakengj_chathead.png?e00b5\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"35\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/Lady_Vulcana_Lovakengj_chathead.png/36px-Lady_Vulcana_Lovakengj_chathead.png?e00b5 1.5x, /images/thumb/Lady_Vulcana_Lovakengj_chathead.png/48px-Lady_Vulcana_Lovakengj_chathead.png?e00b5 2x\" data-file-width=\"65\" data-file-height=\"94\" /></a></span><a href=\"/w/Lady_Vulcana_Lovakengj\" title=\"Lady Vulcana Lovakengj\">Lady Vulcana Lovakengj</a></li>\n<li><span class=\"plink-template\"><a href=\"/w/Councillor_Unkar\" title=\"Councillor Unkar\"><img alt=\"Councillor Unkar chathead.png: Chat head image of Councillor Unkar\"