span><a href=\"/w/Energy_disk\" title=\"Energy disk\">Energy disk</a></li>\n<li><span class=\"plink-template\"><a href=\"/w/Dinh%27s_hammer\" title=\"Dinh&#39;s hammer\"><img alt=\"Dinh&#39;s hammer.png\" src=\"/images/Dinh%27s_hammer.png?4806b\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"29\" height=\"26\" data-file-width=\"29\" data-file-height=\"26\" /></a></span><a href=\"/w/Dinh%27s_hammer\" title=\"Dinh&#39;s hammer\">Dinh's hammer</a></li></ul></td></tr><tr class=\"navbox-group\"><td class=\"navbox-group-title\">Rewards</td><td class=\"navbox-list\">\n<ul><li><span class=\"plink-template\"><a href=\"/w/Lovakengj_favour_certificate\" title=\"Lovakengj favour certificate\"><img alt=\"Lovakengj favour certificate.png\" src=\"/images/Lovakengj_favour_certificate.png?8bd5a\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"31\" height=\"29\" data-file-width=\"31\" data-file-height=\"29\" /></a></span><a href=\"/w/Lovakengj_favour_certificate\" title=\"Lovakengj favour certificate\">Lovakengj favour certificate</a></li>\n<li><span class=\"plink-template\"><a href=\"/w/Jewellery_of_jubilation\" title=\"Jewellery of jubilation\"><img alt=\"Jewellery of jubilation.png\" src=\"/images/Jewellery_of_jubilation.png?de0a9\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"25\" height=\"22\" data-file-width=\"25\" data-file-height=\"22\" /></a></span><a href=\"/w/Jewellery_of_jubilation\" title=\"Jewellery of jubilation\">Jewellery of jubilation</a></li></ul></td></tr><tr class=\"navbox-group\"><td class=\"navbox-group-title\">Locations</td><td class=\"navbox-list\">\n<ul><li><a href=\"/w/Lovakengj\" title=\"Lovakengj\">Lovakengj</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/w/Doors_of_Dinh\" title=\"Doors of Dinh\">Doors of Dinh</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/w/The_Forsaken_Tower_(location)\" title=\"The Forsaken Tower (location)\">The Forsaken Tower</a></li></ul></td></tr><tr class=\"navbox-group\"><td class=\"navbox-group-title\">Scenery</td><td class=\"navbox-list\">\n<ul><li><a href=\"/w/Display_Case_(The_Forsaken_Tower)\" title=\"Display Case (The Forsaken Tower)\">Display Case</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/w/Steam_Generator\" title=\"Steam Generator\">Steam Generator</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/w/Power_Grid\" title=\"Power Grid\">Power Grid</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/w/Furnace_(The_Forsaken_Tower)\" title=\"Furnace (The Forsaken Tower)\">Furnace</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/w/Coolant_Dispenser\" title=\"Coolant Dispenser\">Coolant Dispenser</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/w/Furnace_Coolant\" title=\"Furnace Coolant\">Furnace Coolant</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/w/Table_(The_Forsaken_Tower)\" title=\"Table (The Forsaken Tower)\">Table</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/w/Refinery\" title=\"Refinery\">Refinery</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/w/Energy_Pylon\" title=\"Energy Pylon\">Energy Pylon</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/w/Runic_Altar_(The_Forsaken_Tower)\" title=\"Runic Altar (The Forsaken Tower)\">Runic Altar</a></li></ul></td></tr><tr class=\"navbox-group\"><td class=\"navbox-group-title\">Related</td><td class=\"navbox-list\">\n<ul><li><a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Quick Guide</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/w/Transcript:The_Forsaken_Tower\" title=\"Transcript:The Forsaken Tower\">Transcript</a></li></ul></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nParsed by mediawiki‐67df7655d‐lj2s4\nCached time: 20220421171821\nCache expiry: 3600\nReduced expiry: true\nComplications: []\n[SMW] In‐text annotation parser time: 0.001 seconds\nCPU time usage: 0.167 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.201 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 590/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 34681/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 8197/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 7/100\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 0/5000000 bytes\nLua time usage: 0.019/10.000 seconds\nLua memory usage: 1544663/367001600 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%  143.724      1 -total\n 43.53%   62.560      1 Template:Quest_details_page\n 22.79%   32.759      6 Template:Checklist\n 19.10%   27.447      1 Template:Quest_rewards_page\n 13.08%   18.794      5 Template:Chat_option\n 10.79%   15.510      1 Template:The_Forsaken_Tower\n  8.78%   12.613      1 Template:Navbox\n  6.16%    8.852      7 Template:Ctg\n  3.25%    4.665      1 Template:Quick_Guide\n  2.31%    3.319      1 Template:Fairycode\n-->\n\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key en_osrswiki:pcache:idhash:203691-0!canonical and timestamp 20220421171821 and revision id 14248735. Serialized with PHP.\n -->\n</div>","rawContent":"{{Quick Guide}}\n\n==Details==\n{{Quest details page|The Forsaken Tower}}\n\n==Walkthrough==\n===Start===\n{{Checklist|\n*Talk to [[Lady Vulcana Lovakengj]] in the [[Lovakengj Assembly]] building to the west of the southern bank. {{Chat option|1Yes.|3I'll get going.}}\n*Go to the [[Wintertodt]] camp ([[Games necklace]] teleport).\n**Talk to [[Ignisia]] in the north-east of the camp if you haven't previously done so.\n*Talk to the dwarf [[Undor]] inside the camp. {{Chat option|4 I've been sent to help you.}}\n** If he tells you to talk to the \"Fiery lass\" Talk to Ignisia just to the north east, before returning to him. \n}}\n\n===The Hammer===\n====Powergrid====\n{{Checklist|\n*Go to [[The Forsaken Tower (location)|The Forsaken Tower]] to the east of [[Mount Karuulm]], west of [[Lovakengj]] (north-east of fairy ring {{Fairycode|cir}}, [[Battlefront Teleport]] or [[Skills necklace]] to Farming Guild).\n*Inspect the Display Case.\n*Go down the ladder behind the Display Case and open the north-eastern door. Search the north-north-east crate for a [[generator crank]].\n*Inspect the steam generator in the south. {{Chat option|1 Start the generator.}}\n**Start the generator.\n* Inspect the Power Grid. {{Chat option|1 Yes.}}\n**Align the Power Grid as shown below.\n}}\n[[File:The Forsaken Tower - Powergrid solution.png|center]]\n\n====Furnace====\n{{Checklist|\n*Go up the ladder and then into the northern room. Search the cupboards for a [[tinderbox]], [[5-gallon jug]], and [[8-gallon jug]].\n**Fill the 5-gallon jug with coolant through the coolant dispenser in the west.\n**Use the 5-gallon jug on the empty 8 gallon jug.\n**Fill the 5-gallon jug with coolant.\n**Use the 5-gallon jug on the 8 gallon jug.\n**Empty the 8 gallon jug (right-click check).\n**Use the 5-gallon jug on the empty 8 gallon jug (there should be 2 gallons in the jug).\n**Fill the 5-gallon jug with coolant.\n**Use the 5-gallon jug on the 8 gallon jug.\n**Fill the 5-gallon jug with coolant.\n**Use the 5-gallon jug on the 8 gallon jug.\n**You should now have 4 gallons of coolant in the 5-gallon jug. Use it on the furnace coolant west of the furnace, then light the furnace with the tinderbox.\n*If doing the diary task, smelt the [[adamantite bar]] now.\n}}\n\n====Potion====\n[[File:The Forsaken Tower - old notes explanation.png|thumb|300px|A visual explanation of the solution.]]\n{{Checklist|\n*Go upstairs.\n*Open the door, then take the notes from the eastern cupboard.\n*Take the cleansing fluid from the northern table. '''The position will be random for everyone.''' Look at the notes to see the riddle: the fluids are listed in order of 1-2-3-4-5 (e.g. if cleansing fluid is the second potion mentioned in the fourth sentence, it is number 5).\n**'''Warning''': If you choose the wrong potion, you will take high damage (25+) and become poisoned. This can be avoided by logging out before advancing the dialogue.\n*Use the cleansing fluid on the refinery to the south, then activate it {{Chat option|1 Yes.|1 Yes.}}\n}}\n\n====Altar====\n{{Checklist|* Go up the ladder.\n*There are four discs. In the following order, remove a disc from a pylon and place it on another pylon:\n**From West '''(W)''' to East '''(E)'''\n**From '''W''' to Centre '''(C)'''\n**From '''E''' to '''C'''\n**From '''W''' to '''E'''\n**From '''C''' to '''W'''\n**From '''C''' to '''E'''\n**From '''W''' to '''E'''\n**From '''W''' to '''C'''\n**From '''E''' to '''C'''\n**From '''E''' to '''W'''\n**From '''C''' to '''W'''\n**From '''E''' to '''C'''\n**From '''W''' to '''E'''\n**From '''W''' to '''C'''\n**From '''E''' to '''C'''\n*Go downstairs and get Dinh's hammer from the display case.\n}}\n\n===Finishing up===\n{{Checklist|* Return to [[Wintertodt Camp]].\n*Use the hammer on [[Undor]].\n*Return to [[Lady Vulcana Lovakengj]].\n}}\n\n'''Congratulations, quest complete!'''\n\n==Rewards==\n{{Quest rewards page|The Forsaken Tower}}\n\n{{The Forsaken Tower}}"}